plot: Rachel helps Giuliana with physical therapy exercises. Dolores sees an omen about their ladies' retreat. The husbands host separate nights out with friends. John suffers a medical emergency. Teresa organizes a meeting to confront Margaret.

Rachel helps Giuliana make strides with her motor skills. Dolores receives a sign from the universe regarding the ladies' upcoming peace retreat. The husbands are divided as Louie and Joe Gorga each host their own Guys' Night. At the Gorga house, John experiences a medical emergency. Teresa holds an attorney-led meeting for her friends with the hope of exposing Margaret.
